{
  "stem": "27509.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- the buyer was there, they want, and that was the sort of product that they needed, military uniforms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was a top product that Bialystok produced.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but-- but the orderliness of it was-- was overwhelming, and I remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm writing about it in my book in more detail because it contrasted so much with what happened a little while later when the Russians finally reached Bialystok from-- from the eastern side.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a-- a powwow between them and the Germans at to retreat because they were in Bialystok not according to the agreement.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "According to that agreement, Bialystok belonged to the Russians, not to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they tried to put the Russians before an accomplished situation, but the Russians insisted on their rights according to the agreement.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the way they arrived, in the same manner they've disappeared-- without any impact, orderly, out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then suddenly the first detachment of the Russians arrived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the contrast of the two armies was something that-- that you had to see to understand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] First of all, the Germans were well-fed, beautifully dressed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were victors, their heads high.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no problem about their behavior.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The same streets in which the Polish officers and soldiers used to walk on a Sunday-- the outings were the social life of the-- of the-- of the people took place in the normal way of interaction in-- in those days-- instead of Polish soldiers, German soldiers and German officers were walking.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was no-- no friction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no visible or-- or, as far as I know, any-- any form of-- of aggression and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were very well-behaved.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
